---
title: Rustic Beef & Rosemary Pie with Hidden Veggies & Parmesan Mash Topping
description: Beef and rosemary have always been the flavour couple to beat and there’s nothing that can surpass them when baked into a
golden pie. The homestyle aromas will have your heart and taste buds singing praises all the way through dinner
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66d95cf1673428de49632326-b35de4ff.jpeg
